<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l29">teten vvir allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> /
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> dorothee
